Title: RAVE AM MITTWOCH
content: Das Bangen hat ein Ende, RAM geht weiter!
Ganze 5 Termine stehen uns im Oktober bevor, ab sofort wieder am kompakteren Luster Floor.
Wir danken euch für die unvergessliche Sommer Saison, gemeinsam haben wir den Mittwoch in Wien wieder zum Leben erweckt.
Nun lasst uns schauen, was der Herbst so zu bieten hat, we are f* ready!

Title: HERZFREQUENZ presents: MUGLI PROJECT
content: HARD TECHNO combined with the ART OF DRAG!
THE RAVE with TURBO for a CROWD with a NEED for SPEED!

Founded in 2024, MUGLI PROJECT has quickly established himself as one of the most exciting artists in the Hard Techno scene. With a unique fusion of diverse sounds and a distinctive approach to track construction, he has developed a signature style that sets him apart. In just one year, MUGLI PROJECT has brought his music to some of the world’s biggest stages. His high-energy, driving sound, relentless energy and cutting-edge productions, MUGLI PROJECT is redefining Hard Techno – and this is only the beginning.
HERZFREQUENZ is a SHIRTS OFF RAVE!
This means, that YES: EVERYONE (regardless of GENDER) is ALLOWED TO TAKE OFF their SHIRT!
for Body Shaming | Homophobia | Sexism | Racism | Hate
